                  Notify me when it's live
              div(class="my-4" id="form-msg")
              div(class="mt-4")
                label
                  input(type="checkbox" name="accept_emails" id="accept-emails")
                  span(class="ml-2 text-gray-500 text-xs").
                    Get casual updates on how the development of haptic.so is going on email (1-2 per month, 0% spam!)

      section(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto")
        div(class="mb-4 lg:mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start bg-white shadow-xl p-6 sm:p-12 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl")
          div(class="flex-1 max-w-md")
            h1(class="text-lg sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8") Zero friction
