          div(class="flex-1 max-w-md")
            h1(class="sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8").
              <span class="text-xs block">(Haptic)</span>
                        Feedback
          p(class="sm:text-xl" style="flex: 2").
            Expose your product. Share your journey by finding early adopters and gathering valuable feedback to make your final creation amazing.

        div(class="mb-4 lg:mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start bg-white shadow-xl p-6 sm:p-12 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl")
          div(class="flex-1 max-w-md")
            h1(class="sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8").
              Build your story
          p(class="sm:text-xl" style="flex: 2").
            Good stories always catch people‚Äôs attention. Haptic enables you to build your own product story, share it with your audience and let the makers community support you in growing your startup.

