          div(class="flex-1 max-w-md")
            h1(class="sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8").
              SSOT
          p(class="sm:text-xl" style="flex: 2").
            Haptic is your <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Single_source_of_truth" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="SSOT in Wikipedia" class="link">Single Source Of Truth</a> when it comes to your product evolution. It's all neatly organized, under the haptic.so/( your-product-name ) url.

