          div(class="flex-1 max-w-md")
            h1(class="sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8").
              By creator for creators
          p(class="sm:text-xl" style="flex: 2").
            Haptic is a result of me, struggling to streamline my build in public process. I wanted to fix it. So, here I go.

      section(class="flex items-center justify-center mt-10 sm:mt-40")
        a(
          id="join-btn"
          href="#top"
          class="text-center bg-yellow-300 hover:bg-yellow-400 rounded-xl px-8 sm:text-xl lg:px-12 py-4 lg:py-8 lg:text-xl"
